reviews.review_text:
Help me Rhonda Help me Rhonda is right...jeez, the boys should have let the Beach Boys do it themselves, it sounds like shit.
the rest of the show is good for the time period, no Dogchows and little pig is tolerable.

Pigpen To all you young, little whipersnappers who don't care for the great Ron McKernan, PIGPEN:
1. You don't know what's good
2. You have no clue
3. You just don't get it
So, the bottom line here is those who don't appreciate the great Ron McKernan JUST DON'T GET IT.
